      "note": "publicKeyMultibase omits the 0x02 even-y parity byte: f + e701(varint) + 64-hex x-only = 69 chars (varint ‖ raw-32-byte-x-only, no SEC1 compressed framing). secp256k1-pub (0xe7) is defined over the 33-byte compressed key, so the parity byte is mandatory payload. CI MUST reject (length 69 ≠ 71)."
    },
